  + [proof_pressure] is the condition must be propagated or derived from Navier-Stokes dynamics, not merely assumed
  + [open_shape] is no general theorem proves such alignment/depletion for all smooth 3D data
  + [meaning] is the document's "resonance anchors" become geometric coherence constraints; the missing step is invariance or propagation of coherence

